 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/44/email-notification-in-i3/?answer=45#post-id-45</link><description>I started this discussion on the mailing list some time ago ([here](http://infra.in.zekjur.net/archives/i3-discuss/2012-March/000572.html)), and here is a brief:

a) If you are using an email client: thunderbird or claws-mail will do the trick for you (with tray icon properly displayed as well)

b) If you are only using browser email client, such as Gmail, check out checkgmail.

Update 2013-07-25:

for option (b), checkgmail is basically crashing (project looks dead), so I am dropping it in favor of manually handling this on the i3status directly. You can use conky or add to the i3bar using pipe. I created a script, based on conky solutions for Gmail, it is available here: [gmail-count](https://gist.github.com/brunobraga/6076658) (comments, suggestions, welcome).</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Jun 2012 01:01:35 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/44/email-notification-in-i3/?answer=45#post-id-45</guid></item><item><title>Comment by bruno.braga for &lt;p&gt;I started this discussion on the mailing list some time ago (&lt;a href="http://infra.in.zekjur.net/archives/i3-discuss/2012-March/000572.html"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;), and here is a brief:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a) If you are using an email client: thunderbird or claws-mail will do the trick for you (with tray icon properly displayed as well)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;b) If you are only using browser email client, such as Gmail, check out checkgmail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Update 2013-07-25:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for option (b), checkgmail is basically crashing (project looks dead), so I am dropping it in favor of manually handling this on the i3status directly. You can use conky or add to the i3bar using pipe. I created a script, based on conky solutions for Gmail, it is available here: &lt;a href="https://gist.github.com/brunobraga/6076658"&gt;gmail-count&lt;/a&gt; (comments, suggestions, welcome).&lt;/p&gt;
</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/44/email-notification-in-i3/?comment=2272#comment-2272</link><description>Just released a script I've been using for Gmail, hope it helps: https://gist.github.com/brunobraga/6076658</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2013 05:07:11 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/44/email-notification-in-i3/?comment=2272#comment-2272</guid></item><item><title>Comment by bruno.braga for &lt;p&gt;I started this discussion on the mailing list some time ago (&lt;a href="http://infra.in.zekjur.net/archives/i3-discuss/2012-March/000572.html"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;), and here is a brief:&lt;/p&gt;

